name: Escorted to Runersia
description:
(Second piece in the Isekai Taxi series)
(Wear your headphones for maximum experience)  

A scene where each taxi entering the isekai would get escorted to “Runersia” by a celestial giant orb. What could be waiting there?

As the both world collide, the humans of earth are still slightly visible in the horizon.

2160x2160 seamless looping MP4 with BGM
